reviewText: wow, came so quick and my father was so happy when he received this. Great purchase, awesome seller
a good inside look at the black bird program

The first copy I received was faulty, but Traditional Military Videos replaced it very quickly.

As an SR-71 Blackbird fan, I was extremely disappointed in the video's quality and poor story line. There are better videos in the marketplace and I'd suggest readers check them out over this version.
